reduce it to less than once times perception). Thus at Rank 10 a 4 \x
perception check reduces to 2 \x perception check. The effective Rank
of the spell will be decreased by 1 Rank per 10 miles/hour of wind, to
a minimum of Rank 0, if cast out of doors or in a space where wind is
present.  Below rank 10 the smoke created by this spell is completely
transparent to infravision.
