\begin{college}[1.1]{fire}{Fire Magics}
d3 7
a9 2
The College of Fire Magics is concerned exclusively with shaping the
element of fire.
d11 38
a50 2
The MA requirement for this college is 12.

d52 2
a53 4
an area where it is possible for fire to exist.  The bonuses and
penalties gained in this section apply to non-magical forms of this
element.  Magical forms of the element may at best neutralise any
penalties suffered due to the natural element.
d55 1
a55 2
They may not practice fire magic underwater or in a vacuum, for
example.
d57 3
a59 1
\subsection{Modifiers}
d61 8
a68 2
The following numbers are added to the Base Chance of performing any
talent, spell or ritual of the College of Fire Magics:
d70 2
d73 5
a77 8
Adept is in light mist, fog, or rain		&  -5 \\
Adept is in medium fog, or rain			& -10 \\
Adept is in heavy fog or rain			& -15 \\
Adept is within 30 feet of large campfire	&   5 \\
Adept is within 30 feet of bonfire		&  10 \\
Adept is in contact with small campfire		&   5 \\
Adept is in contact with large campfire		&  10 \\
Adept  is in contact with bonfire		&  15 \\
d79 1
a79 1
