will dissipate at the end of its range. Unless the target successfully
resists they will suffer [D - 5] (+ 1 / Rank) damage from the bolt.
The target's resistance is reduced by 10.  If the target fails to
resist and is flammable or is wearing flammable clothing, then the
flammable possessions of the target will ignite.
