d222 14
a235 8
The spell provides protection from all magical types of fire or fire
spells according to the rank of the spell.  The effective rank of the
fire spell causing the flames or heat is reduced by the rank of this
spell.  For example, if the target is under the effect of this spell
at rank 5, a Hellfire cast at rank 12 will cause damage at an
effective rank of 7.  If the rank of the protection is greater than
the rank of the damaging spell then the target is totally protected
from all effects.
